Here you can find configuration files for the Transifex.net client tool [1] to synchronize translations for GeoServer.org

Steps to activate translation support synchronization for the different projects:

* Install Transifex client tool (http://help.transifex.net/features/client/index.html#getting-the-client)
* checkout GeoServer project from repository
	mkdir gs-trunk
	svn checkout https://svn.codehaus.org/geoserver/trunk
* create a folder '.tx'
	cd gs-trunk
        mkdir .tx
* copy the relevant config file into the '.tx' folder
* start editing on translations
* use the tx client tool to synchronize
